# Test manuel du cron job PayDunya

### Créer une commande test
POST http://localhost:3004/orders/guest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "manual-cron-test@test.com",
  "phoneNumber": "+221775588834",
  "shippingDetails": {
    "firstName": "Manual",
    "lastName": "Cron Test",
    "street": "456 Rue Cron",
    "city": "Dakar",
    "region": "Dakar",
    "country": "Sénégal"
  },
  "orderItems": [{
    "productId": 1,
    "quantity": 1,
    "unitPrice": 8000
  }],
  "totalAmount": 8000,
  "notes": "Test manuel du cron job PayDunya",
  "paymentMethod": "PAYDUNYA",
  "initiatePayment": true
}

###

### Forcer l'exécution du cron job (nécessite token admin)
POST http://localhost:3004/paydunya/cron/run
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Vérifier une commande spécifique (nécessite token admin)
POST http://localhost:3004/paydunya/cron/check/ORD-VOTRE-NUMERO-ICI
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Obtenir les statistiques du cron job (nécessite token admin)
GET http://localhost:3004/paydunya/cron/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE